<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Action Required for Verification</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #F59E0B; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background: #F59E0B; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
        .info-box { background: #FEF3C7; border: 1px solid #FCD34D; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üìã Action Required</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{name}},</h2>
            <p>We're reviewing your student verification request and need some additional information to complete the process.</p>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>Additional Information Needed:</h3>
                <p><strong>{{message}}</strong></p>
                {{#if specificRequirements}}
                <ul style="margin-top: 15px;">
                    {{#each specificRequirements}}
                    <li>{{this}}</li>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <h3>What You Need to Do:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Log into your TalabaHub account</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Go to Verification section</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Provide the requested information</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Re-submit your verification</strong></li>
            </ol>

            <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Complete Verification</a>

            <div style="margin: 30px 0; padding: 20px; background: white; border-radius: 8px;">
                <h4>‚è∞ Timeframe</h4>
                <p>Please provide the requested information within <strong>7 days</strong> to avoid your verification request being closed.</p>

                <h4 style="margin-top: 15px;">üí° Tips</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Ensure documents are clear and readable</li>
                    <li>Make sure all text is visible and not cropped</li>
                    <li>Use recent documents (within 6 months)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Questions?</strong></p>
            <p>If you need help providing the requested information, don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

            <a href="{{supportUrl}}" class="button">Contact Support</a>

            <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
                Your verification request will remain on hold while we wait for your response.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 TalabaHub. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>University Students Platform for Uzbekistan</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>